picograd: torch.Tensor->{PTX, Triton} compiler
disclaimer: this is a one man effort to compile llama2. beware of dragons.
models:
  system 1 (autoregressive sequence learning):
    sequential:
      - nn (bengio et al. 2003)
      - rnn (mikolov et al. 2010)
      - gru (kyunghyun cho et al. 2014)
      - wavenet (oord et al. 2016)
    parallel (vaswani et al. 2017):
      - gpt2 (raford et al. 2018, 2019, 2020)
      - llama2 (touvron et al. 2023)
  system 2 (___ search):
  continuous learning:
  meta learning:
  todo: vae, gan, diffusion, ebm
